<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Joy's Colorful Corner</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', cursive, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4, #fbc2eb, #a6c1ee);
      background-size: 400% 400%;
      animation: gradientBG 10s ease infinite;
      color: #333;
    }

    @keyframes gradientBG {
      0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
      50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
      100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 3em;
      margin: 0;
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 1.2em;
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 15px;
      padding: 15px;
    }

    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: white;
      color: #333;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      transform: scale(1.1);
      background: #ffecd2;
    }

    section {
      margin: 30px;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .projects div, .skills span {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 5px;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      background: #fff;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .projects div:hover, .skills span:hover {
      transform: rotate(-3deg) scale(1.05);
      background: #ffe0f0;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
    }

    .contact a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 5px;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 10px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .contact a:hover {
      background: #d4fc79;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <header>
    <h1>🌈 Joy's Colorful Corner</h1>
    <p>A tiny chaotic universe of thoughts, projects, and vibes ✨</p>
  </header>

  <nav>
    <a href="#about">About Me</a>
    <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
    <a href="#skills">Skills</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
  </nav>

  <section id="about">
    <h2>💫 About Me</h2>
    <p>
      Hi! I'm Joy — a human with too many thoughts and not enough tabs to store them.
      I like building things, overthinking everything, and occasionally making life decisions at 2AM.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="projects" class="projects">
    <h2>🚀 Projects</h2>
    <div>Water Filter Business 💧</div>
    <div>Content Creator 🎥</div>
    <div>Random Late Night Ideas 🌙</div>
  </section>

  <section id="skills" class="skills">
    <h2>🛠 Skills</h2>
    <span>Marketing</span>
    <span>Video Editing</span>
    <span>Overthinking</span>
    <span>Surviving Mondays</span>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" class="contact">
    <h2>📬 Contact</h2>
    <a href="#">Instagram</a>
    <a href="#">Email</a>
    <a href="#">TikTok</a>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>Made with chaos & caffeine ☕</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
